  author    = {Amunts, Katrin and Angenent, Sigurd and Annese, Jacopo and Bharatha, Aditya and Cheney, Paul and Cherry, Simon and Cohen, Lawrence and Dailey, Michael and Devous, Michael and Sr and Duimstra, Joseph and Erinjeri, P and Falk, Chun and Friston, Karl and Gambhir, Sanjiv and Gevins, Alan and Gonzalez, R and Guimond, Alexandre and Haker, Steven and Hamalainen, Matti and Hari, Riitta and Heinz, Karl and Jacobs, Russell and Jolesz, Ferenc and Kikinis, Ron and Louie, Angelique and Mandeville, Joseph and Maudsley, Andrew and Meade, Thomas and Mega, Michael and Mori, Susumu and Narasimhan, P and Pa, Nicola and Omero-Gallagher, / and Pascual, Alvaro and Paus, Tomas and Phelps, Michael and Pommert, Andreas and Pouratian, Nader and Rexilius, Jan and Roche, Alexis and Rosen, Bruce and Schleicher, Axel and Vogt, O and Sundaresan, Gobalakrishnan and Talos, Florin and Tannenbaum, Allen and Tei, Alida and Thompson, Paul and Ugurbi, Kamil and Vii, Arno and Wachowiak, Matt},
