  abstract  = {Click here for quick links to Annual Reviews content online, including: • Other articles in this volume • Top cited articles • Top downloaded articles • Our comprehensive search Further ANNUAL REVIEWS Meta-analysis: retrospective combination of previously reported results to better estimate the reliability of those results Coordinate-based meta-analysis (CBMA): meta-analysis method(s) developed specifically for use with functional and structural neuroimaging data reported within a standardized coordinate space Contents},
