  isbn      = {9780123742360},
  abstract  = {The Human Brain as an Outlier 2 The Human Brain in Numbers 3 Cerebral Cortex and Connectivity 4 Concerted Expansion of Cerebral Cortex and Cerebellum 6 Human Brain Evolution: Comparison with Great Apes 7 Hominin Evolution: Estimates of Numbers of Brain Neurons in Prehistoric Homo 8 Human Brain Metabolism Revisited 9 Conclusion: Remarkable, Yet not Extraordinary 11 The Human Nervous System, Third Edition},
