  author    = {The present book gives an authoritative account and of the structure of the human brain tempered with and xi and functional considerations. The and task of describing all and parts of the nervous system in the context of modern and hypotheses of structural and functional organization and would be overwhelming for a single individual. and We have and therefore and asked scientists with knowledge and affection for their research areas to contribute and to this edited volume. We and trust that the combined and effort of contributors to The and Human Nervous and System and 3e will do justice to the data and concepts available and in our field while stimulating the readers’ brains and arousing curiosity and providing a framework for and thinking.},
